        "AI"
      ],
      "versionName": "1.0.2",
      "fullDescription": "Nemotron 3 Nano 30B-A3B (Hybrid Mamba-Transformer MoE, 3.5B active) served via llama.cpp — optimized for Olares One.\nRTX 5090M (24GB) + 96GB DDR5 + Core Ultra 9 275HX.\nUnsloth Dynamic Q4_K_XL quantization (important layers upcasted to 8/16-bit).\nHybrid architecture: 23 Mamba-2 layers + 6 GQA attention layers + MoE FFN.\nFlash attention, CUDA graph optimization, and op-offload enabled.\nBuilt-in reasoning mode with think/no-think toggle via chat template.\nDownloads the GGUF model on first launch (~23GB) and caches it.\nExposes an OpenAI-compatible API on port 8080.\n",
