      "fullDescription": "Qwen3.5 35B-A3B Vision (MoE, 3B active) served via llama.cpp — optimized for Olares One.\nMultimodal: accepts images via OpenAI-compatible vision API (image_url format).\nRTX 5090M (24GB) + 96GB DDR5 + Core Ultra 9 275HX.\nUnsloth Dynamic Q4_K_XL quantization (22.2GB) + mmproj F16 (0.9GB).\nFlash attention, CUDA graph optimization, and op-offload enabled.\nllama.cpp b8334 with multimodal projector support.\nDownloads the GGUF model (~22GB) and mmproj (~0.9GB) on first launch.\nContext reduced to 16K to fit model + mmproj in 24GB VRAM.\nExposes an OpenAI-compatible API on port 8080.\n",
